Name: _Status
Expression:
IF(
    'DB_PROCUREMENT_CONTRACT contracts_new'[Expired_Date] > TODAY() ||
    'DB_PROCUREMENT_CONTRACT contracts_new'[Expired_Date] = 'DB_PROCUREMENT_CONTRACT contracts_new'[Contract_Date] ||
    ISBLANK('DB_PROCUREMENT_CONTRACT contracts_new'[Expired_Date]),
    "Active",
    "Closed"
)

Name: _Active
Expression:
VAR CurrentDate = TODAY()
VAR ThisContractNumber = Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number]
VAR ThisVersion = Combined_Contracts[Amendment_Version]

VAR MaxVersion =
    CALCULATE(
        MAX(Combined_Contracts[Amendment_Version]),
        FILTER(
            Combined_Contracts,
            Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number] = ThisContractNumber
        )
    )

VAR LatestExpiry =
    CALCULATE(
        MAX(Combined_Contracts[Expired_Date]),
        FILTER(
            Combined_Contracts,
            Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number] = ThisContractNumber &&
            Combined_Contracts[Amendment_Version] = MaxVersion
        )
    )

RETURN
IF (
    ThisVersion = MaxVersion &&
    CurrentDate < LatestExpiry,
    "Active",
    "Closed"
)

Name: _CheckAmandemented
Expression:
VAR CurrentContract = combined_contracts[Contract_Number]
VAR TotalVersions =
    CALCULATE(
        COUNTROWS(combined_contracts),
        FILTER(
            combined_contracts,
            combined_contracts[Contract_Number] = CurrentContract
        )
    )
RETURN
IF(TotalVersions > 1, "Yes", "No")

Name: _MaxExpired
Expression:
VAR ContractNumber = Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number]
VAR MaxED =
    CALCULATE(
        MAX(Combined_Contracts[Expired_Date]),
        FILTER(
            Combined_Contracts,
            Combined_Contracts[Contract_Number] = ContractNumber
        )
    )
RETURN
IF(MaxED > TODAY(), 1, 0)
